ght=3D"4128"></a><figcaption>Kyra Sedgwick and Kevin Bacon during The Best =
You Can premiere at the 2025 Tribeca Festival</figcaption></figure>
<p>Bacon has been married to actress <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Kyra_Sedgwick" title=3D"Kyra Sedgwick">Kyra Sedgwick</a> since September=
 4, 1988; they met on the set of the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/PBS" title=3D"PBS">PBS</a> version of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/wiki/Lanford_Wilson" title=3D"Lanford Wilson">Lanford Wilson</a>'s play <=
i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lemon_Sky" title=3D"Lemon Sky">L=
emon Sky</a></i>. He has said: "The time I was hitting what I considered to=
 be bottom was also the time I met my wife, our kids were born, good things=
 were happening. And I was able to keep supporting myself; that always gave=
 me strength."<sup id=3D"cite_ref-cosmo91_10-1" class=3D"reference"><a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-cosmo91-10"><span c=
lass=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>10<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></=
sup> Bacon and Sedgwick have starred together in <i><a href=3D"https://en.w=
ikipedia.org/wiki/Pyrates" title=3D"Pyrates">Pyrates</a>,</i> <i><a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murder_in_the_First_(film)" title=3D"Murder =
in the First (film)">Murder in the First</a></i>, <i><a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Woodsman_(2004_film)" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D=
"The Woodsman (2004 film)">The Woodsman</a></i>, and <i><a href=3D"https://=
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loverboy_(2005_film)" title=3D"Loverboy (2005 film)">=
Loverboy</a></i>. They have two children, Travis Sedgwick (born 1989) and <=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sosie_Bacon" title=3D"Sosie Bacon">=
Sosie Ruth</a> (born 1992). They reside on the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/Upper_West_Side" title=3D"Upper West Side">Upper West Side</a>=
 of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manhattan" title=3D"Manhattan"=
>Manhattan</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-51" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https=
://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-51"><span class=3D"cite-brac=
ket">[</span>51<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> Bacon was pr=
eviously in a five-year relationship with actress <a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Tracy_Pollan" title=3D"Tracy Pollan">Tracy Pollan</a>, in t=
he 1980s.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-52" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-52"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[=
</span>52<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p><p>Bacon has spoken out for the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wik=
i/Separation_of_church_and_state_in_the_United_States" title=3D"Separation =
of church and state in the United States">separation of church and state</a=
>,<sup id=3D"cite_ref-53" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikiped=
ia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-53"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>=
53<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-54" cl=
ass=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite=
_note-54"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>54<span class=3D"cite-bracke=
t">]</span></a></sup> and told <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/=
The_Times" title=3D"The Times">The Times</a></i> in 2005 that he <a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atheism" title=3D"Atheism">did not "believe =
in God."</a><sup id=3D"cite_ref-55" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://=
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-55"><span class=3D"cite-bracket=
">[</span>55<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> He has also sai=
d that he is not <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antireligion" tit=
le=3D"Antireligion">anti-religion</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-56" class=3D"refe=
rence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-56"><=
span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>56<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span>=
</a></sup>
</p><p>Bacon and Sedgwick appeared in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Will.i.am" title=3D"Will.i.am">will.i.am</a>'s video <a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/It%27s_a_New_Day_(Will.i.am_song)" class=3D"mw-redir=
ect" title=3D"It's a New Day (Will.i.am song)">"It's a New Day"</a>, which =
was released following <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barack_Obam=
a" title=3D"Barack Obama">Barack Obama</a>'s 2008 presidential win.<sup cla=
ss=3D"noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style=3D"white-space:nowrap;">=
[<i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" tit=
le=3D"Wikipedia:Citation needed"><span title=3D"This claim needs references=
 to reliable sources. (June 2025)">citation needed</span></a></i>]</sup>
</p><p>The pair lost part of their savings in the <a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Ponzi_scheme" title=3D"Ponzi scheme">Ponzi scheme</a> of in=
famous swindler <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bernie_Madoff" tit=
le=3D"Bernie Madoff">Bernie Madoff</a>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-financialpost_57=
-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Baco=
n#cite_note-financialpost-57"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>57<span =
class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-58" class=3D"r=
eference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-58=
"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>58<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</sp=
an></a></sup>
</p><p>Bacon and Sedgwick learned in 2011, via their appearance on the PBS =
TV series <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Finding_Your_Roots" t=
itle=3D"Finding Your Roots">Finding Your Roots</a></i> with <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_Louis_Gates" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D=
"Henry Louis Gates">Henry Louis Gates</a>, that they are ninth cousins, onc=
e removed.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-59" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-59"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">=
[</span>59<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> They also appeare=
d in a video<sup id=3D"cite_ref-60" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://=
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_note-60"><span class=3D"cite-bracket=
">[</span>60<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> promoting the "=
Bill of Reproductive Rights", supporting among other things a woman's right=
 to choose and have access to birth control.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-61" class=
=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Bacon#cite_no=
te-61"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>61<span class=3D"cite-bracket">=
]</span></a></sup>
</p>
